body:
Hello,

    I've been working on this resource pack recently, and would like to get some feedback before releasing it. I've only made a few textures myself, but I've mixed textures from a bunch of different packs. I'm working on crediting the people.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nvf5qF7Bw9g&feature=youtu.be

I'd like to get some feedback before releasing. Enjoy! :D
